'''塞浦路斯大瘟疫'''（{{lang-en|Plague of Cyprian}}）是一場[[大流行病|大流行病]]，大約在公元AD 249年至262年間發生於[[羅馬帝國|羅馬帝國]]。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=harper>{{cite web |url=https://www.theatlantic.com/science/archive/2017/11/solving-the-mystery-of-an-ancient-roman-plague/543528/ |title=Solving the Mystery of an Ancient Roman Plague |work=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] |last=Harper |first=Kyle |date=1 November 2017 |access-date=2 December 2017 |archive-date=2021-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217165226/https://www.theatlantic.com/science/archive/2017/11/solving-the-mystery-of-an-ancient-roman-plague/543528/ }}</ref> 人們普遍認為瘟疫造成糧食生產和羅馬軍隊的廣泛人力短缺，在[[三世紀危機|三世紀危機]]嚴重削弱了帝國<ref name="Zosimus">{{cite book | title=The New History, Book 1 | publisher=Green and Chaplin | access-date=2016-04-22 | last=Zosimus | author-link=Zosimus (historian) | orig-year=translation originally printed | others=(scanned and published online by Roger Pearse) | url=http://www.tertullian.org/fathers/zosimus01_book1.htm | year=1814 | location=London | pages=16, 21, 31 | archive-date=2008-05-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514173519/http://www.tertullian.org/fathers/zosimus01_book1.htm }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LOjqWL-u9VMC&pg=PA62#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=The power of plagues by Irwin W. Sherman |access-date=2022-02-06 |archive-date=2021-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518142933/https://books.google.com/books?id=LOjqWL-u9VMC&pg=PA62#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>。 它的現代名稱是為紀念早期的基督教作家{{le|迦太基主教|Archdiocese of Carthage}}[[居普良|圣西普里安]]，他見證並描述了瘟疫。 由於來源稀少，瘟疫的誘因並不能確定，但病因可能有包括[[天花|天花]]，流行性流感和[[埃博拉出血热|埃博拉出血热]]等病毒<ref name=harper/>。

塞浦路斯大瘟疫的具体死亡人数未知，但据记载罗马城每日有5000人死于该瘟疫。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Plague of Cyprian, 250-270 CE|url=https://www.ancient.eu/article/992/plague-of-cyprian-250-270-ce/|accessdate=2020-12-07|work=Ancient History Encyclopedia|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117181942/https://www.ancient.eu/article/992/plague-of-cyprian-250-270-ce/}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Solving the Mystery of an Ancient Roman Plague|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/science/archive/2017/11/solving-the-mystery-of-an-ancient-roman-plague/543528/|accessdate=2020-12-07|date=2017-11-01|last=Harper|first=Kyle|work=The Atlantic|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217165226/https://www.theatlantic.com/science/archive/2017/11/solving-the-mystery-of-an-ancient-roman-plague/543528/}}</ref>

